snippet.title: Hen, Chicks And Cats - Trailer [Gameplay]
snippet.description:
HEN, CHICKS AND CATS' is a fun logic puzzle game where you have to think before you move, one wrong move and the hen 'Ju' could fall into traps or run into an unfriendly cat. The hen is scared, so it won't stop running until it bumps into something, so think before you run around. 

https://www.risingmoongames.com/our-games/hen-chicks-and-cats
